codemirror.theme.*.js files are forked from https://github.com/fsegurai/codemirror-themes/ (MIT)
and modified to fit the needs of this extension.

The following styles are removed:
- Panels
- Line numbering
- Gutter elements
- Diff/merge view styles
- Deleted/removed content styles
- Focus outline
- Lint points
- Selections:
  - `z-index` on .cm-selectionLayer
  - `color` on .cm-selectionBackground
- max-height on .cm-tooltip-autocomplete (Tokyo Night, VSCode)

Note that following these changes, some color variables become unused and so are removed.

The following styles are modified:
- Matching brackets: targets `.cm-matchingBracket, &.cm-focused .cm-matchingBracket`
  instead of just `.cm-matchingBracket`, and same for `.cm-nonmatchingBracket`.
- `invalid` tag:
  - Material: borderBottom is removed.
  - All themes except Material: textDecoration is removed, borderBottom style changed to `dotted`.
